name: Eviction Week
description:
[THIS GAME CONTAINS EXPLICIT REFERENCES TO PERIODS AND MENSTRUATION. IF SUCH CONTENT OFFENDS YOU, TURN AWAY NOW.]

Your least favorite task from inside where you work involves needing to expel a bunch of unwilling, stubborn "tenants". Because the methods you may have to resort to will surely cause a lot discomfort for the entire infrastructure...

Directly inspired by other "inner mechanics" stories such as Cells at Work! and Osmosis Jones.
